RAM, HardDisk, special configurations).

If you want to get a newer - and maybe debugged - version of SViewIV
do not forget to register as an user of SViewIV with the included
registration form.
Nevertheless unregistered users are as welcome to report bugs as
users who decide(d) to register.

@ENDNODE

